{"tid":186294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"村民收60蚊幫遊客翻牆入動物園 落地即聽見獅吼","createTime":"2017-04-04T06:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T00:12:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9134afe4f89bbc93ea440d6b70db6c1ce952f468","tid":186294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:08:30.000Z","msg":"2017年04月04日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170403/large/1491229371_c065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170403%2Flarge%2F1491229371_c065.jpg&h=ae112bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國人實在唔怕死！浙江寧波早前有人為逃130元（人民幣．下同）的入場券，翻牆進入動物園最後被老咬死，近日在陝西西安一個動物園，竟有人收錢，拿長梯助人進入動物園以節省40元，有民眾翻牆入園後，竟然聽到幾聲獅吼，嚇得心驚膽跳。<br />\n涉事的是西安的秦嶺野生動物園，在動物園附近的圍牆外，有當地村民招攬生意，稱只要付60元，便可籍長近4米的梯，翻牆入園，不用買門券。<br />\n在村民的帶路下，想逃票的民眾在圍牆外準備，當村民見沒有保安員巡查時，便搭起長梯，民眾逐一翻牆，進入園區，他們的落點是動物園的「蟲蟲世界」，村民臨走時特別指示，不要到海洋表演場和馬戲大世界等要查票的項目。<br />\n不過，一名姓王的民眾沒這樣好彩，之前他也是貪小便宜，翻牆進入動物園，沒想到他們落點卻是猛獸區，一落地便聽到遠處傳來兩聲獅子吼聲，十分嚇人。<br />\n動物園的保安稱，周邊的村民組織這樣的逃票團，他們都無辦法追查，客服中心人員則稱，民眾要是逃票進入動物園，後果自負。<br />\n「95%以上中國人的德行，自己為了省幾個錢，貪圖點小便宜，反倒給老虎，獅子送免費餐！」網民除指摘村民組織這種翻牆旅行團，亦批評逃票民眾寧可花錢冒險，都不願買票：「有便宜就沾，出了人命就訛，沒有點做人的底線，臉都沒了！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170404/56515478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170404%2F56515478&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ccf1dd30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170404%2F56515478&h=bef3e787\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170404/56515478</a>"},{"pid":"5765190716c3de0657b9fdc6509b4c7089a720bc","tid":186294,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6e077eaf7ccb49ed55c2fbaf4b50585ea5ccc91","tid":186294,"uid":16978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"實體翻牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a0dbc941dc17191bef5f5ef59645f4ef384fb5","tid":186294,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"食人肉毛色靚好多"},{"pid":"7d3b1e124fddb0a1ffd01fa7883d6af33865b51a","tid":186294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b912570aa60540e3ed272d83725c7c267ae4c449","tid":186294,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"似有仇口累死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169bcbadabab97f4cf1eacad1754a593def56f80","tid":186294,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"支那人就係賤"},{"pid":"bda5de294236b8f950d8498db0d6301f633f7f9f","tid":186294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03242c13ffe2f81f35dfb8da4791a7f0d0252376","tid":186294,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0024999c1445164ee2224bc9dceef4aa2d74340","tid":186294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae71148f5c6f43a7d61ea4ab801adafc7214b73b","tid":186294,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:49:58.000Z","msg":"動物園管理層：冇錢買肉比獅子食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下屬：我扮村民，之後咁咁咁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6cc809a293cac127c36ee13a84ed75cb953249","tid":186294,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物園管理層：冇錢買肉比獅子食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下屬：我扮村民，之後咁咁咁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果度係餵飼區，不對外開放，食咗都冇人知架！"},{"pid":"83c3db3a9221f64c107f09137638045fc49a7d2d","tid":186294,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:12:24.000Z","msg":"動物園僱用附近村民，帶為省門票的民衆翻牆，牆的背後為野生動物餵飼區。"}]}